<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Nosuchelementexception on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/nosuchelementexception/</link><description>Recent content in Nosuchelementexception on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/nosuchelementexception/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Kotlin NoSuchElementException — Element Not Found Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/nosuchelement-kotlin/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/nosuchelement-kotlin/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="nosuchelementexception--element-not-found"&gt;NoSuchElementException — Element Not Found&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;NoSuchElementException&lt;/code&gt; occurs when you try to access an element that doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist in a collection or iterator.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kotlin collections throw &lt;code&gt;NoSuchElementException&lt;/code&gt; when you use methods like &lt;code&gt;first()&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;last()&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;elementAt()&lt;/code&gt; on empty collections or when the element isn&amp;rsquo;t found.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common causes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Empty collection access&lt;/strong&gt; — calling &lt;code&gt;first()&lt;/code&gt; on empty list&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Missing iterator element&lt;/strong&gt; — accessing beyond iterator bounds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Map key not found&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;code&gt;map.getValue()&lt;/code&gt; with missing key&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Set element missing&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;code&gt;set.element()&lt;/code&gt; with non-existent element&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Empty collection
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; empty = emptyList&amp;lt;Int&amp;gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;empty.first() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NoSuchElementException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Iterator bounds
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; list = listOf(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; iterator = list.iterator()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;iterator.next() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;iterator.next() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;iterator.next() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;iterator.next() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NoSuchElementException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Map key not found
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; map = mapOf(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;a&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; to &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; to &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;map.getValue(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;c&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NoSuchElementException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Single element on empty
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; empty = emptyList&amp;lt;Int&amp;gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;empty.single() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NoSuchElementException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-use-firstornull--lastornull"&gt;Fix 1: Use &lt;code&gt;firstOrNull&lt;/code&gt; / &lt;code&gt;lastOrNull&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; empty = emptyList&amp;lt;Int&amp;gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;empty.first() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Exception
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; first = empty.firstOrNull() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-elementatornull"&gt;Fix 2: Use &lt;code&gt;elementAtOrNull&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; list = listOf(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;list.elementAt(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Exception
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;list.elementAtOrNull(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-getorelse-for-maps"&gt;Fix 3: Use &lt;code&gt;getOrElse&lt;/code&gt; for maps&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; map = mapOf(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;a&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; to &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;map.getValue(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;c&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Exception
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; value = map.getOrElse(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;c&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) { &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-check-before-access"&gt;Fix 4: Check before access&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; list = listOf(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;list.first() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Works, but risky if empty
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (list.isNotEmpty()) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; first = list.first()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Safe element access
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; numbers = listOf(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; first = numbers.firstOrNull() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 10
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; missing = numbers.firstOrNull { &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;it&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// null
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Safe map access
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; config = mapOf(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;host&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; to &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;localhost&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; port = config[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;port&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;toIntOrNull() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;8080&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/index-out-of-bounds/"&gt;IndexOutOfBoundsException&lt;/a&gt; — index beyond bounds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/nullpointer-kotlin/"&gt;NullPointerException&lt;/a&gt; — null dereference&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/illegal-argument/"&gt;IllegalArgumentException&lt;/a&gt; — invalid argument&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>